Picabot
=======

Install Picabot:

  $ gem install picabot

Then install required optimizer binaries:

  https://github.com/toy/image_optim#binaries-installation

Run Picabot help:

  $ picabot -h

Get your token at https://github.com/settings/tokens/new and use your username:

  $ picabot --user somu --token h03niea942fl509zc8

After this run, you can run it without any flags:

  $ picabot

Use id flag to move your Picabot pointer to newer repos:

  $ picabot --id 12000000

Picabot loves concurrency:
  
  $ picabot --workers 3